le="font-weight: 400;">Lucidia&#8217;s ultimate goal is to provide its customers with a fully immersive online environment in which they can study, work, play, shop, and interact while also utilizing their digital avatar. All that&#8217;s required to join Lucidia is a quick app download and registration. Once that&#8217;s done, they&#8217;re free to explore Lucidia at their leisure.</span></p>						</div>
